<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .access-denied-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .access-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #4e73df;
            border-color: #4e73df;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #2e59d9;
            border-color: #2e59d9;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="access-denied-container">
        <div class="access-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
            ⚠️
        </div>

        <h2 class="mb-3">Truy cập bị từ chối</h2>

        <p class="lead">
            <%= message %>
        </p>

        <p>Vui lòng đăng nhập với tài khoản quản trị viên để tiếp tục.</p>

        <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-block">
            <a href="/taikhoan/dang-nhap" class="btn btn-primary">Đăng nhập</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary ms-md-2">Quay lại trang chủ</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>